reviewText:
Early Access Review

Brilliant game, if you enjoyed Titan quest you wil love this game.

as with any ARPG the key elements to success are

1) build variety;
2) enjoyment in progressing through the acts;
3) end game (what keeps you coming back even once you've reached max level);

This game does the first two very well and the third looks to be on track as well as the game develops.

Well done to the small development team in achieving what D3, poe and T2 couldnt - at least for me.
